data.description: Beautiful, recently updated 4 bedroom Countryside home w/ 2500+ sq. ft of living space, 2 car garage, and basement! Spacious floor plan with room for all and great for entertaining. The open kitchen boasts brand new SS appliances and bar stool seating. Massive owners suite with space to unwind. Basement is perfect for playroom, working out, or your finishing touches. New Roof and siding (2022). You'll love the private backyard with mature trees. Community amenities - two pools, playground, tennis courts, pond, and miles of walking trails. Nearby award-winning Oak Trace Elementary School.
